<item>
            <title>[LU-126] missing check_failover_pair in some tests of mmp.sh </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-126</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In mmp.sh, there is no check_failover_pair in the beginning of test 8-10, which might create some fake results when there is no failover-setup there. Though I am not so sure about this. Can some one please check that?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10446">LU-126</key>
            <summary>missing check_failover_pair in some tests of mmp.sh </summary>
